----------------------------------------------------------------
 IMPORTANT NOTES
----------------------------------------------------------------

  - The site runs on XAMPP (Apache + MySQL). Both Apache and
    MySQL must be running for the site to work.

  - The admin account is hardcoded — it does not exist in the
    database. It is checked directly in login.php.

  - Tutor profiles are auto-created on signup so new tutors
    are immediately visible for messaging, even before admin
    approval.

  - Unapproved tutors show a "Pending Approval" badge in the
    booking section and cannot be booked until approved.

  - All background images, uploaded photos, and PDFs are
    stored in the /image/ folder.

  - Dark/light mode is handled by theme.js and theme.css and
    persists across pages using localStorage.

  - Session authentication uses sessionStorage — logging out
    or closing the browser clears the login session.


